#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn16.7"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn16.7:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 16 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 16 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn16.7:0.2"
msgid "1. Kassapavagga "
msgstr "1. Kassapa "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn16.7:0.3"
msgid "7. Dutiyaovādasutta "
msgstr "7. Advice (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.206, sc1
#. VAR: veḷuvane → sāvatthiyaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "sn16.7:1.1"
msgid "Rājagahe viharati veḷuvane. "
msgstr "Near Rājagaha, in the Bamboo Grove. "

msgctxt "sn16.7:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā mahākassapo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami … pe … "
msgstr "Then Venerable Mahākassapa went up to the Buddha, bowed, and sat down to one side. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn16.7:1.3"
msgid "ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho āyasmantaṃ mahākassapaṃ bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "The Buddha said to him, "

msgctxt "sn16.7:1.4"
msgid "“ovada, kassapa, bhikkhū; "
msgstr "“Kassapa, advise the mendicants! "

msgctxt "sn16.7:1.5"
msgid "karohi, kassapa, bhikkhūnaṃ dhammiṃ kathaṃ. "
msgstr "Give them a Dhamma talk! "

msgctxt "sn16.7:1.6"
msgid "Ahaṃ vā, kassapa, bhikkhū ovadeyyaṃ tvaṃ vā; "
msgstr "Either you or I should advise the mendicants "

msgctxt "sn16.7:1.7"
msgid "ahaṃ vā bhikkhūnaṃ dhammiṃ kathaṃ kareyyaṃ tvaṃ vā”ti. "
msgstr "and give them a Dhamma talk.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn16.7:2.1"
msgid "“Dubbacā kho, bhante, etarahi bhikkhū, dovacassakaraṇehi dhammehi samannāgatā akkhamā appadakkhiṇaggāhino anusāsaniṃ. "
msgstr "“Sir, the mendicants these days are hard to admonish, having qualities that make them hard to admonish. They’re impatient, and don’t take instruction respectfully. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: hirī → hiri (sabbattha)
#. VAR: āgacchati → āgacchanti (si)
msgctxt "sn16.7:2.2"
msgid "Yassa kassaci, bhante, saddhā natthi kusalesu dhammesu, hirī natthi kusalesu dhammesu, ottappaṃ natthi kusalesu dhammesu, vīriyaṃ natthi kusalesu dhammesu, paññā natthi kusalesu dhammesu, tassa yā ratti vā divaso vā āgacchati, hāniyeva pāṭikaṅkhā kusalesu dhammesu, no vuddhi. "
msgstr "Sir, whoever has no faith, conscience, prudence, energy, or wisdom when it comes to skillful qualities can expect decline, not growth, in skillful qualities, whether by day or by night. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn16.7:3.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhante, kāḷapakkhe candassa yā ratti vā divaso vā āgacchati, hāyateva vaṇṇena, hāyati maṇḍalena, hāyati ābhāya, hāyati ārohapariṇāhena. "
msgstr "It’s like the moon in the waning fortnight. Whether by day or by night, its beauty, roundness, light, and diameter and circumference only decline. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn16.7:3.2"
msgid "Evameva kho, bhante, yassa kassaci saddhā natthi kusalesu dhammesu … pe … "
msgstr "In the same way, whoever has no faith, conscience, prudence, energy, and wisdom when it comes to skillful qualities can expect decline, not growth, in skillful qualities, whether by day or by night. "

msgctxt "sn16.7:3.3"
msgid "hirī natthi … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn16.7:3.4"
msgid "ottappaṃ natthi … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn16.7:3.5"
msgid "vīriyaṃ natthi … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn16.7:3.6"
msgid "paññā natthi … kusalesu dhammesu tassa yā ratti vā divaso vā āgacchati, hāniyeva pāṭikaṅkhā kusalesu dhammesu, no vuddhi. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn16.7:4.1"
msgid "‘Assaddho purisapuggalo’ti, bhante, parihānametaṃ; "
msgstr "A faithless individual is in decline. "

msgctxt "sn16.7:4.2"
msgid "‘ahiriko purisapuggalo’ti, bhante, parihānametaṃ; "
msgstr "An individual with no conscience is in decline. "

msgctxt "sn16.7:4.3"
msgid "‘anottappī purisapuggalo’ti, bhante, parihānametaṃ; "
msgstr "An imprudent individual is in decline. "

msgctxt "sn16.7:4.4"
msgid "‘kusīto purisapuggalo’ti, bhante, parihānametaṃ; "
msgstr "A lazy individual is in decline. "

msgctxt "sn16.7:4.5"
msgid "‘duppañño purisapuggalo’ti, bhante, parihānametaṃ; "
msgstr "A witless individual is in decline. "

msgctxt "sn16.7:4.6"
msgid "‘kodhano purisapuggalo’ti, bhante, parihānametaṃ; "
msgstr "An irritable individual is in decline. "

msgctxt "sn16.7:4.7"
msgid "‘upanāhī purisapuggalo’ti, bhante, parihānametaṃ; "
msgstr "A hostile individual is in decline. "

msgctxt "sn16.7:4.8"
msgid "‘na santi bhikkhū ovādakā’ti, bhante, parihānametaṃ. "
msgstr "When there are no mendicant advisers there is decline. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn16.7:5.1"
