msgstr "Sir, whoever has faith, conscience, prudence, energy, and wisdom when it comes to skillful qualities can expect growth, not decline, in skillful qualities, whether by day or by night. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.207, sc6
